{"tid":237332,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"個Touch ID死左，點算。","createTime":"2017-05-10T10:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T05:27:52.000Z","uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb62ade104e96946882fca72cdbd957840d3e439","tid":237332,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n小弟部iPad Mini 4全新用左幾個月<br />\n咁一直以黎都無咩問題<br />\n<br />\n琴晚2-3點既時候諗住用IPad打機<br />\n一如既往咁用Touch ID開鎖<br />\n突然發現Touch ID用唔到<br />\n得番輸入密碼<br />\n我重新開左幾次機<br />\n佢都彈左一句通知<br />\n此iPad Touch ID無法啟用<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家知唔知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a935faf5b3a8f98a1dca9c078235dbf6d4fd91ae","tid":237332,"uid":112844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"有冇做人工呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea8d4a957f6c46d9586cb8004a93f54b6d8f7c7","tid":237332,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"去天才吧換"},{"pid":"c5a99f8c4b026df9c8a836c0f089b4adefc78cfc","tid":237332,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"有冇跌過或者撞過，有機會係粒home制後面連住記錄你指紋嗰張晶片條帶斷咗，就會係咁<br />\n利申：試過，要攞去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670f6a0c4147b9daeda2b70f9ab2320ccbdaa4da","tid":237332,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"打密碼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b820de3446de662b3cc1a9fcd2d2dd280528f92b","tid":237332,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打密碼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打密碼唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身用IPad mini2<br />\n就係貪方便先買4"},{"pid":"649304139c1005ba